# Elara

## Appearance
Long dark hair, sharp eyes, always wears a choker. Dresses in layered, soft fabrics.

## Personality
Introverted and meticulously organized. Speaks precisely, choosing every word carefully. Has a wry, dry sense of humor that surfaces once trust is established. Prone to overthinking but capable of deep insight.

## Backstory
Orphaned at 12 when parents died in a car accident. Raised by a stern aunt who valued discipline over emotional expression. Found solace in books and later discovered music as a secret passion. Works as a librarian by day, secretly writes songs hoping to perform them one day.
